e: ￹`O~ `tadamaan~`ay~ `a~ `tilid~ `konini~.￺This is very important / special writing.￻這是很重要的文件/特別的文件
￹`O~ `tilid~ `ni~`~ `Pa~`wlo~ `konini~.￺These are Paul's writings.￻這是保羅的書信
￹`Pa~`tilid~`en~ `ni~`~ `Pa~`wlo~ `ko~ `salikaka~ `no~ `Loma~.￺Paul wrote to the brothers in Rome.￻保羅寫信給在羅馬的信徒
￹`O~ `maan~ `ko~ `ma~`tilid~`ay~ `iso~.￺What have you written?￻你寫的是什麼？
￹`O~ `ci~`tilid~`ay~ `a~ `kiradom~ `konini~.￺This cloth is patterned.￻這件布料是樣本
